      "Title": "EXE 文件（使用 Py 安装程序）在不同的计算机上不起作用 | EXE file (using Py installer) does not work in different computer",
      "Link": "https://dev.to/khanalim/exe-file-using-py-installer-does-not-work-in-different-computer-4lno",
      "Description": "\u003cdiv id=\"page-content-inner\"\u003e\u003cp class=\"crayons-layout\"\u003e\u003cmain id=\"main-content\" class=\"crayons-layout__content grid gap-4\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-wrapper\"\u003e\u003carticle class=\"crayons-card crayons-article mb-4\" id=\"article-show-container\"\u003e\u003cheader class=\"crayons-article__header\" id=\"main-title\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__header__meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex s:items-start flex-col s:flex-row\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex flex-1 mb-5 items-start\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"relative\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/khanalim\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"radius-full align-middle\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--KFDUtDsU--/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_50,q_auto,w_50/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/979826/eaa52650-a66c-446e-84a8-5f8990d9701d.png\" width=\"40\" alt=\"卡纳林\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"pl-3 flex-1\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/khanalim\" class=\"crayons-link fw-bold\"\u003e卡纳林\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp class=\"fs-xs color-base-60\"\u003e发表于\u003ctime class=\"date-no-year\"\u003e您好，我使用 PyCharm 作为我的文本编辑器，并使用“auto-py-to-exe”从 python 脚本创建了一个可执行文件。 在我的电脑上一切正常。 我正在使用 Mac。 但是，当我将带有文件夹的 exe 文件传输到另一台 pc 或 Mac 时，该计算机甚至无法将 exe 文件识别为可执行文件。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 我完全迷路了。 谁能建议我什么？ \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/main\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection class=\"crayons-card crayons-card--secondary text-padding mb-4 print-hidden\" id=\"bottom-content-read-next\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"军事个人资料图片\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--4YoIzUym--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/647509/6a2025d3-9842-40a4-a6da-2ea225aadb8a.jpeg\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"宣传资料图片\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--qu0RnCdR--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/286811/54d3506c-8230-451b-b76d-3fd4b8fce165.png\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"bilawal_maskeen 个人资料图片\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--Rtdzkc5z--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/979364/6a13db0a-ccc1-44c8-98f6-5d796e18d8d4.png\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"诺萨尼个人资料图片\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--228s6mC2--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/741231/ea92baeb-4f3b-4f96-992c-2b20fb41babd.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"suspend-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 一旦暂停，khanalim 将无法发表评论或发布帖子，直到他们的暂停被解除。\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"unsuspend-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 解除暂停后，khanalim 将能够再次发表评论和发布帖子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"unpublish-all-posts\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 一旦取消发布，khanalim 的所有帖子都将隐藏起来，只有他们自己可以访问。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"mt-2\"\u003e 如果 khanalim 没有被暂停，他们仍然可以从他们的仪表板重新发布他们的帖子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"mt-2\"\u003e \u003clabel\u003e笔记：\u003c/label\u003e \u003ctextarea id=\"note_content\" class=\"crayons-textfield note_content\"\u003e\u003c/textarea\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"flag-user-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 感谢您保护 DEV 社区 👩‍💻👨‍💻 的安全。 以下是标记 khanalim 的方法：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"crayons-field\"\u003e\u003cinput type=\"radio\" id=\"flag-user-radio-input\" class=\"crayons-radio\"\u003e \u003clabel class=\"crayons-field__label\"\u003e降低 khanalim 的所有帖子的可见度\u003c/label\u003e\u003cp class=\"crayons-field__description\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"javascript:void(0);\" id=\"report-inappropriate-content\"\u003e报告其他不当行为\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"unflag-user-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e取消标记 khanalim 将恢复其帖子的默认可见性。\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n原文: \u003cdiv id=\"page-content-inner\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"crayons-layout\"\u003e \u003cmain id=\"main-content\" class=\"crayons-layout__content grid gap-4\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"article-wrapper\"\u003e \u003carticle class=\"crayons-card crayons-article mb-4\" id=\"article-show-container\"\u003e \u003cheader class=\"crayons-article__header\" id=\"main-title\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__header__meta\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex s:items-start flex-col s:flex-row\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex flex-1 mb-5 items-start\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"relative\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/khanalim\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"radius-full align-middle\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--KFDUtDsU--/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_50,q_auto,w_50/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/979826/eaa52650-a66c-446e-84a8-5f8990d9701d.png\" width=\"40\" alt=\"khanalim\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"pl-3 flex-1\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/khanalim\" class=\"crayons-link fw-bold\"\u003ekhanalim\u003c/a\u003e \u003cp class=\"fs-xs color-base-60\"\u003e Posted on \u003ctime class=\"date-no-year\"\u003eNov 27\u003c/time\u003e \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/header\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__main\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__body text-styles spec__body\" id=\"article-body\"\u003e \u003cp\u003eHello,\nI use PyCharm as my text editor and created an executable file from python script using \"auto-py-to-exe\". Everything works in my computer. I am using Mac. However, when I transfer the exe file with folder to another pc or Mac, that computer does not even recognize the exe file as an executable file.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\nI am totally lost. Can anyone suggest me anything?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/main\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003csection class=\"crayons-card crayons-card--secondary text-padding mb-4 print-hidden\" id=\"bottom-content-read-next\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/milandry/standing-on-the-shoulders-of-giants-the-articles-and-resources-that-have-shaped-my-career-26b6\" class=\"crayons-link mt-6 block\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e \u003cimg alt=\"milandry profile image\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--4YoIzUym--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/647509/6a2025d3-9842-40a4-a6da-2ea225aadb8a.jpeg\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/promode/7-steps-to-become-an-automation-tester-step-by-step-way-to-switch-from-manual-to-automation-1d6o\" class=\"crayons-link mt-6 block\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e \u003cimg alt=\"promode profile image\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--qu0RnCdR--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/286811/54d3506c-8230-451b-b76d-3fd4b8fce165.png\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/bilawal_maskeen/piers-morgan-blasts-prince-harry-meghan-for-attacking-monarchy-says-shame-on-kerry-kennedy-2i2l\" class=\"crayons-link mt-6 block\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e \u003cimg alt=\"bilawal_maskeen profile image\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--Rtdzkc5z--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/979364/6a13db0a-ccc1-44c8-98f6-5d796e18d8d4.png\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/nothanii/top-5-ways-to-monetize-your-mobile-application-2776\" class=\"crayons-link mt-6 block\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e \u003cimg alt=\"nothanii profile image\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--228s6mC2--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/741231/ea92baeb-4f3b-4f96-992c-2b20fb41babd.jpg\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e \u003c/section\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"suspend-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Once suspended, khanalim will not be able to comment or publish posts until their suspension is removed. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"unsuspend-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Once unsuspended, khanalim will be able to comment and publish posts again. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"unpublish-all-posts\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Once unpublished, all posts by khanalim will become hidden and only accessible to themselves. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"mt-2\"\u003e If khanalim is not suspended, they can still re-publish their posts from their dashboard. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"mt-2\"\u003e\u003clabel\u003eNote:\u003c/label\u003e\u003ctextarea id=\"note_content\" class=\"crayons-textfield note_content\"\u003e\n\u003c/textarea\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"flag-user-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Thanks for keeping DEV Community 👩‍💻👨‍💻 safe. Here is what you can do to flag khanalim: \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"crayons-field\"\u003e \u003cinput type=\"radio\" id=\"flag-user-radio-input\" class=\"crayons-radio\"\u003e \u003clabel class=\"crayons-field__label\"\u003e Make all posts by khanalim less visible \u003cp class=\"crayons-field__description\"\u003e khanalim consistently posts content that violates DEV Community 👩‍💻👨‍💻's code of conduct because it is harassing, offensive or spammy. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/label\u003e \u003c/p\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"mt-4\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"javascript:void(0);\" id=\"report-inappropriate-content\"\u003e Report other inappropriate conduct \u003c/a\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"unflag-user-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Unflagging khanalim will restore default visibility to their posts. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e",
