      "Title": "在法留学生，凭我的个人资料能找到比外包公司更好的工作吗？ | Foreign student in France, can I find a better job than outsourcing companies with my profile?",
      "Link": "https://dev.to/kokoro_aya/foreign-student-in-france-can-i-find-a-better-job-than-outsourcing-companies-with-my-profile-49h1",
      "Description": "\u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__body text-styles spec__body\" id=\"article-body\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是一名在法国大学学习计算机专业的留学生，想找一份体面的工作。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 我知道在法国，大多数工作机会都是由臭名昭著的外包公司提供的，这些公司名声不好。 然而，其他学生经常说他们更喜欢这些公司，因为他们提供了一些在技术行业现实生活中的第一次体验。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 好吧，恕我直言，我怀疑这种经验的价值，因为他们可能会研究许多过时的技术，而新来的学生别无选择——在我看来，这是一个陷阱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 问题来了——根据我的个人资料，我能否在一家更体面的公司寻求更好的机会？ 我能不能给我一些建议，比如我应该专注于哪个领域来提高我的表现？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 我在 GitHub 上有几个个人项目，包括我在大学三年级时工作的项目，用 ANTLR/Kotlin/React 或 Unity “创建一个人们编写代码来引导角色四处移动和行动的游戏” .\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 还有关于编译或语言的东西，但我承认它们相当混乱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 我也在一家勤工俭学的公司工作，但由于一些难以公开的原因，我不打算留在这家公司。 因此，我想知道是否有可能在客户端/前端或 3d 编程等领域找到工作机会。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 此外，上周我们学校组织了一场比赛，目的是开发一个应用程序来可视化一些数据并与它们互动。 我之所以选择 Flutter，是因为我更希望有一个同时适用于 iOS/macOS 和 Android 的应用程序。 然而我之前对Flutter一无所知。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 这是一周后的产品（使用了很多库，但我花了一些时间来调整小部件并尝试做出更好的视觉设计，我还使用了 MVVM 来获得更好的架构）：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--K9axnm1w--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/05hb92enyrc8l0hg6dc6.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--K9axnm1w--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/05hb92enyrc8l0hg6dc6.png\" alt=\"我的应用截图\" width=\"880\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 我也在从事其他几个个人项目，尽管我不得不承认在面试中我可以炫耀的东西不多。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 因此我想知道我是否有可能找到一个体面的机会而不是为一家法国外包公司工作。 如果我想加入一家初创公司，是否真的很难处理 CDI 和签证问题？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 感谢您的阅读和任何可能的建议！\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n原文: \u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__body text-styles spec__body\" id=\"article-body\"\u003e \u003cp\u003eI am a foreign student learning computer science in a French university and I would like to find a decent job.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eI know that in France, most job opportunities are offered by the infamous outsourcing companies, that has long records of bad reputation. However, often other students say that they prefer these companies as they offer some first experiences in real life in the technology industry.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eWell, IMHO, I doubt for the value of such experience as they likely work on numerous obsolete technologies and fresh new students don't have a choice - in my opinion it's rather a trap.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eHere is the problem - with my profile, can I seek for a better possibility in a more decent company? Could I have some advices such like which field should I focus on to enhance my performance?\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eI have several personal projects on GitHub, including the one that I worked when I was in the 3rd year of bachelor, to \"create a game where people write code to direct characters to move around and act\" with ANTLR/Kotlin/React or Unity.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eThere are also things about compiling or languages but I admit that they are quite a messy.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eI am also working for a company under the work-study program but I don't expect to stay in this company due to several reasons hard to disclose to the public. I am therefore wondering if it's possible to find an offer in fields such like client/front-end or 3d programming.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eBesides, last week our school organised a contest to develop an app to visualise some data and interact with them. I had chosen Flutter since I would prefer to have an app that works on both iOS/macOS and Android. However I didn't know anything about Flutter before.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eHere's the production in one week (many libraries were used but I had taken time for adaptions of widgets and tried to make a better visual design, I also used the MVVM for a better architecture):\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--K9axnm1w--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/05hb92enyrc8l0hg6dc6.png\" class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--K9axnm1w--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/05hb92enyrc8l0hg6dc6.png\" alt=\"my app screenshot\" width=\"880\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eI am also working on several other personal projects though I have to admit that there's not much things that I could show off during an interview.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eTherefore I would like to know if it's possible for me to find a decent opportunity instead of working for a French outsourcing company. Could it be really difficult to deal with the CDI and visa problems if I would like to join a startup?\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eThank you for your reading and any possible advices!\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e",
      "Author": "kokoro_aya",
      "PubDate": "2022-11-26T23:49:27.00000001Z"
    },
    {
      "Title": "开源分析仪表板 | Open Source Analytics Dashboard",
      "Link": "https://dev.to/theplugjumbo/open-source-analytics-dashboard-4cck",
      "Description": "\u003cdiv id=\"page-content-inner\"\u003e\u003cp class=\"crayons-layout\"\u003e\u003cmain id=\"main-content\" class=\"crayons-layout__content grid gap-4\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"article-wrapper\"\u003e\u003carticle class=\"crayons-card crayons-article mb-4\" id=\"article-show-container\"\u003e\u003cheader class=\"crayons-article__header\" id=\"main-title\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__cover\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--LOCjVkWH--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_420,q_auto,w_1000/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/awd0l7ofqn78w3pbhr8l.png\" width=\"1000\" class=\"crayons-article__cover__image\" alt=\"开源分析仪表板的封面图片\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__header__meta\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex s:items-start flex-col s:flex-row\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex flex-1 mb-5 items-start\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"relative\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/theplugjumbo\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"radius-full align-middle\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--lPlU_W9---/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_50,q_auto,w_50/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/875511/5a16bd81-7109-41a6-bb05-85e0bc9cc13e.jpeg\" width=\"40\" alt=\"布兰登\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/header\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__main\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__body text-styles spec__body\" id=\"article-body\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 下午好！ 今天，我很高兴地宣布\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/ThePlugJumbo/openops\"\u003eOpenOps\u003c/a\u003e ，一个开源的、自托管的 Next.js 业务仪表板。 我刚刚开始这个项目，正在寻找贡献者。 如果您有兴趣，请查看\u003ca href=\"https://github.com/ThePlugJumbo/openops/issues\"\u003eGitHub 问题\u003c/a\u003e并随时提交拉取请求。 \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"crayons-card crayons-card--secondary crayons-sponsorship-article text-styles\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 我希望我的这篇文章会激怒所有人：反 JavaScript 斗士们，对我们在现代网站上大量使用的东西感到震惊； 人们争论网络无论如何都是交互式应用程序的破平台，我们应该重新开始；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e 反应用户； 使用手工 JS 和手工编写的 HTML 的守旧派； 和 Tom MacWright，自从多年前我第一次知道他在 Mapbox 上的工作以来，我一直很钦佩他。 但我想这就是发表意见的代价。 \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003csection class=\"crayons-card crayons-card--secondary text-padding mb-4 print-hidden\" id=\"bottom-content-read-next\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"jmfayard 个人资料图片\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--uYDGIy63--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/17066/483c36ce-ca15-45f9-ab16-fbe032dda0b1.jpeg\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp class=\"opacity-75 pt-1\"\u003e 让-米歇尔法亚德🇫🇷🇩🇪🇬🇧🇪🇸⇨🇴 -\u003ctime\u003e 一旦被暂停，theplugjumbo 将无法发表评论或发布帖子，直到他们的暂停被取消。\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"unsuspend-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 解除暂停后，theplugjumbo 将能够再次发表评论和发布帖子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"unpublish-all-posts\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 一旦取消发布，theplugjumbo 的所有帖子都将隐藏起来，只有他们自己可以访问。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"mt-2\"\u003e 如果 theplugjumbo 没有被暂停，他们仍然可以从他们的仪表板重新发布他们的帖子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"mt-2\"\u003e \u003clabel\u003e笔记：\u003c/label\u003e \u003ctextarea id=\"note_content\" class=\"crayons-textfield note_content\"\u003e\u003c/textarea\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"flag-user-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e 感谢您保护 DEV 社区 👩‍💻👨‍💻 的安全。 以下是标记 theplugjumbo 的方法：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"crayons-field\"\u003e\u003cinput type=\"radio\" id=\"flag-user-radio-input\" class=\"crayons-radio\"\u003e \u003clabel class=\"crayons-field__label\"\u003e降低 theplugjumbo 的所有帖子的可见度\u003c/label\u003e\u003cp class=\"crayons-field__description\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"javascript:void(0);\" id=\"report-inappropriate-content\"\u003e报告其他不当行为\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"unflag-user-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e取消标记 theplugjumbo 将恢复其帖子的默认可见性。\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n原文: \u003cdiv id=\"page-content-inner\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"crayons-layout\"\u003e \u003cmain id=\"main-content\" class=\"crayons-layout__content grid gap-4\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"article-wrapper\"\u003e \u003carticle class=\"crayons-card crayons-article mb-4\" id=\"article-show-container\"\u003e \u003cheader class=\"crayons-article__header\" id=\"main-title\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__cover\"\u003e \u003cimg src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--LOCjVkWH--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_420,q_auto,w_1000/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/awd0l7ofqn78w3pbhr8l.png\" width=\"1000\" class=\"crayons-article__cover__image\" alt=\"Cover image for Open Source Analytics Dashboard\"\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__header__meta\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex s:items-start flex-col s:flex-row\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex flex-1 mb-5 items-start\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"relative\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/theplugjumbo\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"radius-full align-middle\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--lPlU_W9---/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_50,q_auto,w_50/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/875511/5a16bd81-7109-41a6-bb05-85e0bc9cc13e.jpeg\" width=\"40\" alt=\"Brandon\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/header\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__main\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"crayons-article__body text-styles spec__body\" id=\"article-body\"\u003e \u003cp\u003eGood afternoon! Today, I am happy to anounce \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/ThePlugJumbo/openops\"\u003eOpenOps\u003c/a\u003e, an open source, self hosted Next.js business dashboard. OpenOps is a new tool that allows you to bring Google Analytics, PayPal, Stripe, and more into one UI.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eI am just starting out on this project, and am looking for contributors. If you are interested, check out the \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/ThePlugJumbo/openops/issues\"\u003eGitHub issues\u003c/a\u003e and feel free to submit a pull request.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/article\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"crayons-card crayons-card--secondary crayons-sponsorship-article text-styles\"\u003e \u003cp\u003eI expect I'll annoy everyone with this post: the anti-JavaScript crusaders, justly aghast at how much of the stuff we slather onto modern websites; the people arguing the web is a broken platform for interactive applications anyway and we should start over;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eReact users; the old guard with their artisanal JS and hand authored HTML; and Tom MacWright, someone I've admired from afar since I first became aware of his work on Mapbox many years ago. But I guess that's the price of having opinions.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003csection class=\"crayons-card crayons-card--secondary text-padding mb-4 print-hidden\" id=\"bottom-content-read-next\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/jmfayard/git-is-not-the-end-of-history-42f0\" class=\"crayons-link mt-6 block\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e \u003cimg alt=\"jmfayard profile image\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--uYDGIy63--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/17066/483c36ce-ca15-45f9-ab16-fbe032dda0b1.jpeg\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e \u003cdiv\u003e \u003cp class=\"opacity-75 pt-1\"\u003e Jean-Michel Fayard 🇫🇷🇩🇪🇬🇧🇪🇸🇨🇴 - \u003ctime\u003eNov 24\u003c/time\u003e \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/mjmaix/boilerplate-for-nestjs-terraform-aws-lambda-with-lazy-module-loading-1nf1\" class=\"crayons-link mt-6 block\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e \u003cimg alt=\"mjmaix profile image\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--XVHjbYpS--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/142403/8011c2ef-f3d9-451a-a1a6-df1b8c26725a.jpeg\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/egeaytin/fine-grained-access-control-where-rbac-falls-short-37hp\" class=\"crayons-link mt-6 block\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e \u003cimg alt=\"egeaytin profile image\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--jg1AeSdd--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/922857/1957dc3e-c85f-4603-9e8a-ae41a7e69961.jpeg\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/sm0ke/django-soft-design-free-pypi-library-18fa\" class=\"crayons-link mt-6 block\"\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"flex items-center\"\u003e \u003cspan class=\"crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0\"\u003e \u003cimg alt=\"sm0ke profile image\" class=\"crayons-avatar__image\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--5FUUPuaB--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/152613/f6aadb36-121c-409f-b746-e40e0408ea51.png\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e \u003c/section\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/main\u003e \u003c/p\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"suspend-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Once suspended, theplugjumbo will not be able to comment or publish posts until their suspension is removed. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"unsuspend-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Once unsuspended, theplugjumbo will be able to comment and publish posts again. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"unpublish-all-posts\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Once unpublished, all posts by theplugjumbo will become hidden and only accessible to themselves. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"mt-2\"\u003e If theplugjumbo is not suspended, they can still re-publish their posts from their dashboard. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"mt-2\"\u003e\u003clabel\u003eNote:\u003c/label\u003e\u003ctextarea id=\"note_content\" class=\"crayons-textfield note_content\"\u003e\n\u003c/textarea\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"flag-user-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Thanks for keeping DEV Community 👩‍💻👨‍💻 safe. Here is what you can do to flag theplugjumbo: \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"crayons-field\"\u003e \u003cinput type=\"radio\" id=\"flag-user-radio-input\" class=\"crayons-radio\"\u003e \u003clabel class=\"crayons-field__label\"\u003e Make all posts by theplugjumbo less visible \u003cp class=\"crayons-field__description\"\u003e theplugjumbo consistently posts content that violates DEV Community 👩‍💻👨‍💻's code of conduct because it is harassing, offensive or spammy. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/label\u003e \u003c/p\u003e \u003cdiv class=\"mt-4\"\u003e \u003ca href=\"javascript:void(0);\" id=\"report-inappropriate-content\"\u003e Report other inappropriate conduct \u003c/a\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"unflag-user-modal-content\" class=\"hidden\"\u003e \u003cp\u003e Unflagging theplugjumbo will restore default visibility to their posts. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e",
